Package hashtables

Class HumanBeingManager

java.lang.Object
hashtables.HumanBeingManager
All Implemented Interfaces:
HashtableManager<Long,HumanBeing>
public class HumanBeingManager extends Object implements HashtableManager<Long,HumanBeing>
Current implementation of the HashtableManager that has a Long values as keys and HumanBeing objects as values.
